---
title: Data Flow & DTO Transformations
---
flowchart LR
    subgraph DB["Database"]
        Row["Prisma Entity\n─────────\nid: string\nname: string\ntarget_size_usd: Decimal\nstatus: FundStatus enum\ncreated_at: Date\nupdated_at: Date"]
    end

    subgraph Repo["Repository"]
        Raw["{ data: Fund[]\n  total: number }"]
    end

    subgraph Service["Service — DTO Mapping"]
        DTO["FundResponseDto\n─────────\nid: string\nname: string\ntarget_size_usd: number  ← .toNumber()\nstatus: string\ncreated_at: string       ← .toISOString()\nupdated_at: string       ← .toISOString()"]
        Paginated["PaginatedResponse\n─────────\ndata: FundResponseDto[]\ntotal: number\npage: number\nlimit: number\ntotalPages: number"]
    end

    subgraph Controller["Controller"]
        JSON["res.json(result.value)"]
    end

    DB -->|prisma.$transaction| Repo
    Repo -->|toFundResponseList| DTO
    DTO -->|buildPaginatedResponse| Paginated
    Paginated -->|Result.ok| JSON

    subgraph Input["Inbound — Request Body"]
        ZOD["Zod Schema\nvalidateBody/parse\n─────────\nname: string 1-255\nvintage_year: int\ntarget_size_usd: number\nstatus?: enum"]
    end

    ZOD -->|CreateFundInput| Service
